Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能 文森特·罗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.32,0:25:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直追寻的真实
